<br>
DG somehow unintentionally hurt UI to some degree. It's just plain wrong.<br>
<br>
Nobody in DG intentionally trained UI. Yes I do know this for a fact, no matter how much you say I don't know Gailen and my other guildies.<br>
<br>
True that DG should have offered to help UI CR, but note that according to Yaara, DG could not handle our own CR (she had to eventually rez Gailen) so it seems like that this wan't an option.<br>
